<br/>
<br/>
<h2 id="cedar-ui-libraries" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#cedar-ui-libraries">#</a> Cedar UI libraries</h2>
<p>There are a number of Figma UI libraries that house the Cedar design system. These libraries, as well as a few others, will be pre-loaded when you create a new file within the REI Figma ecosystem. In order to take advantage of all that Cedar offers, doublecheck to make sure that these libraries are turned on (and turn off libraries from other teams that you might not need).</p>
  <cdr-img alt="" :src="$withBase(`/getting-started-for-designers/libraries.png`)"/>
<p>For more information on Cedar UI libraries, check out <a href="https://www.figma.com/file/9V46NiDSDfg1crbdOKpIVN/Turning-on-Libraries%3A-Tutorial?node-id=0%3A1" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">this tutorial<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> about turning on library assets in Figma.</p>
